modules.description: This module implements a read-only key-value store interface with operations to query, retrieve, and inspect stored values. It works with string keys and values, supporting partial reads, metadata queries (like size, digest, and modification time), and directory-style listings. Concrete use cases include serving static assets from a pre-built store and validating content digests in a MirageOS unikernel.

This module implements a read-only key-value store interface with operations to check key existence, retrieve values, and inspect metadata like size, digest, and modification time. It works with string keys and values, supporting partial reads and directory-like structures via key prefixes. Concrete use cases include serving static assets from a prebuilt store or validating content digests in a distributed system.

This module provides two implementations of a read-only key-value store interface. Both work with string keys and values, supporting key existence checks, value retrieval, metadata inspection (size, digest, modification time), and directory-style operations via prefixes or listings. They are used for serving static assets and validating content digests in environments like MirageOS unikernels or distributed systems.
